steps.name: New User Setup: Free User Sign up
Create new user data
Free user sign up API call
New User Setup: Free User Email Confirmation via Database
New User Setup: Free User Login
Fill in Email Address
Fill in Password
Click on the Login Button
New User Setup: Upgrade Free User to Business
Click the Settings on the Side Menu
Click on the Billing option in the side menu
Click "Upgrade" button for Business option
Enter card details
Enter card number
Enter expiration date
Enter CVC
Enter Full Name
Enter ZIP
Click "Subscribe" button
Click "No,thanks" button on the One Time Special Offer Modal
A toast message with the text "Plan has been successfully changed." is visible and hidden then
Click "Sign" sidemenu
Click the Settings on the Side Menu
Click API on Horizontal Menu
Click on the "Create API key" button at the right
Fill in the "API key name" field
Click "Create API" button
Click "Copy API" button
Wait the toast appears indicating API key has been successfully copied to clipboard
Verify the toast message that API key has been successfully copied to clipboard
Ensure the API key is not empty
Retrieve API key value
Ensure the API key is not undefined
Retrieve API key value
Click close button at the API modal window
Paste into the "Billing Details" field with Ctrl+V shortcuts
Verify that pasted API key matches the one created with "Create API" button on the right.
